  "title": "Relationship Manager (Trade finance)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Establish and maintain close relationships with potential and existing clients which include: Corporate customers and other financial institutional</li><li>Implement marketing plans, new deals and products initiated by Department Head</li><li>Prepare and present new credit applications with credit and market analysis to credit committee</li><li>Prepare credit reviews/renewals/memorandum for existing clients</li><li>Prepare and submit all necessary credit applications and relevant documentations to Head Office for approval</li><li>Providing portfolio management for existing facilities to ensure complete compliance with KYC, AML and terms of approval in the bank's credit policy</li><li>Act as the main liaising point between external clients and internal departments for clients’ business requirements and queries</li><li>Raise day to day new trade transaction approvals</li><li>Prepare month-end reporting for management and Head Office</li><li>Participate in ad- hoc projects in the Bank as assigned by the manager</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>At least 3 years of working experience in the related field</li><li>Sound knowledge of trade finance products and corporate business.</li><li>Familiar with UCP, ISP 98 and URC regulations</li></ul><p><strong>HOW TO APPLY:</strong></p><p>Interested applicants, please click on <strong>“Apply Now”</strong> or submit your resume to <a href=\"mailto:ref71@trustrecruit.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>ref71@trustrecruit.com.sg</strong></a></p><p><br /></p><p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p><br /></p><p>Important Note: Trust Recruit Pte Ltd is committed to safeguarding your personal data in accordance with the Personal Data Protection Act (PDPA).</p><p>Please read our privacy statement on our corporate website <a href=\"http://www.trustrecruit.com.sg/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">www.trustrecruit.com.sg</a>.</p><p><br /></p><p>Trust Recruit Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 19C9950</p><p>EA Personnel: Lee Jia Xiang</p><p>EA Personnel Reg No: R25158171</p>",
